* Iron Raptor had recieved the image of herself, finding that she really did 
look like an overgrown human felame with blue skin and white hair.
But none of it looked bad, not at all.
Though, she did feel really different without her armor...she had never been 
really naked before.
But besides her image she also felt love from Prowl, even more then before. 
Feeling them as almost the same thing from him. Her and love.

But soon the itch on her nose began to get worse and she brought her breath 
in, stepping out of Prowls arms and trying to pinch her nose to stop the 
sneeze...but it was too late.
Iron Raptor covered her nose, and closed her eyes, sneezing a bit hard.
But just as suddenly as she sneezed something happened, something 
surprising....
Out from behind her shoulders sprouted two long, full white wings. Feathers 
drifting from them to catch on the breeze and drift all around both Prowl 
and herself.
Stretching out to thrie limits until equalling more then 3 times be body 
length.
Iron Raptor leaned back, looking towards Prowl as the wind picked up and 
blew her hair in waves. Feathers floating on the wind, catching currents and 
floating away.*
